addWeaponPool 
Game: Operation Flashpoint: Resistance (1.75) 
Description: Add weapons to the weapon pool, of which the player may choose in the following 
 mission. Available in campaigns only.  
Syntax:  
 addWeaponPool [weaponName, count] 
Parameters: 
[weaponName, count]: Array 
weaponName: String - weapon name. See the topic Category:Weapons for reference about possible values. 
count: Number - number of weapons to add 
Return Value: 
 Nothing